{{ESC National Year | Year = 1995 | Country = Bosnia and Herzegovina | Preselection = BH Eurosong 1995 | Entrant = [[Davorin Popović]] | Song = [[Dvadeset prvi vijek]] | Final result = 19th, 14 points }} '''Bosnia and Herzegovina''' participated in the '''Eurovision Song Contest 1995''' in [[Dublin]], Ireland. [[Davorin Popović]] represented Bosnia and Herzegovina with the song "[[Dvadeset prvi vijek]]". They finished on 19th place out of 23 countries with 14 points.
